text: Meadow Lake Power Station is a natural gas-fired station owned by SaskPower, located in Meadow Lake, Saskatchewan, Canada and operated as a peaking plant. == Description == The Meadow Lake Station consists of:Plant Description * 1 - 44 MW unit, commissioned in 1984 == See also == * SaskPower ==References== == External links == * SaskPower Station Description Category:Meadow Lake, Saskatchewan Category:Natural gas-fired power stations in Saskatchewan Category:SaskPower
title: Meadow Lake Power Station
